description:
This user story came from customer support team. 

Primary reason is to get more users for feature XXXX

Needed tasks:

Design, Implement, Document and Deployment

Acceptance criterias:

-Review help documentation with end user customer
-Check user can disable feature without extra cost
-User can choose which credit(s) to pick up
-I can see my new purse balance when I have chosen to pick up a credit
summary: As a (type of user), I want (to perform some task) so that I can (achieve some goal/benefit/value).
